reference to legislation,
I think FDR passed 76 laws in
the first 100

28:10.955 --> 28:13.925 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
days through a very amenable
Congress.

28:13.958 --> 28:19.497 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Obviously, Trump is not going to
come anywhere
near that record, and probably
no other president

28:19.531 --> 28:21.433 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
will either.

28:21.466 --> 28:25.904 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
