executive orders,
on the Supreme Court appointment
of Neil Gorsuch,

28:25.937 --> 28:31.976 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
he gets A's in terms of getting
what he wanted
based on some of the promises
that he made

28:32.010 --> 28:33.344 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
during the campaign.

28:33.378 --> 28:35.146 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Michael, how do
you see him
compared to others?

28:35.180 --> 28:38.283 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MICHAEL BESCHLOSS: I think I
would say it
a little differently, because
Trump made such

28:38.316 --> 28:42.554 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
