pretty low down on the list.

29:18.056 --> 29:23.094 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, Barbara,
Michael referenced
where this 100-day standard
comes from, but

29:23.128 --> 29:27.065 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
