Voting Rights
Act of 1965, so we will point to
a president

29:51.990 --> 29:53.324 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
like that.

29:53.358 --> 29:57.262 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Again, no one will ever again
standard of
FDR in legislation.

29:57.295 --> 30:02.867 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I also look out where they come
out in the
first 100 days on approval
ratings, which

30:02.901 --> 30:05.236 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
