play.

30:05.270 --> 30:09.174 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
We know this president coming
in, of course,
came in with the lowest entering
approval

30:09.207 --> 30:11.109 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
