with my base.

31:33.825 --> 31:35.593 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
I will play to them.

31:35.627 --> 31:41.132 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I am not going to make a big
effort to reach
out to Democrats and
independents in Congress

31:41.165 --> 31:43.001 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
or out among the American
people.

31:43.034 --> 31:45.603 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And I think the numbers show
that he's paid
for that.

31:45.637 --> 31:52.143 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: One other feature
of this presidency
has been his unusual attacks, if
you will,

31:52.176 --> 31:53.945 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
Barbara, on the judiciary.

31:53.978 --> 31:59.083 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
