32:00.919 --> 32:04.055 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
BARBARA PERRY: He has, which is
a little odd,
in the sense that his sister is
a federal

32:04.088 --> 32:06.891 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
judge, and a circuit judge at
that.

32:06.925 --> 32:11.362 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But he is following in the
footsteps of some
other presidents, and we can
point directly

32:11.396 --> 32:17.635 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
to FDR, for example, who took on
the judiciary
headlong, not necessarily even
in the first

32:17.669 --> 32:22.040 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
