32:23.975 --> 32:27.812 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But I always go back to a speech
that he gave
in which he said, the two
branches of government,

32:27.845 --> 32:29.781 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
president and Congress, are
pulling a wagon.

32:29.814 --> 32:33.418 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
