many pieces of
New Deal legislation, is pulling
in the opposite

32:38.022 --> 32:39.324 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
direction.

32:39.357 --> 32:41.159 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
That was a metaphor that the
American people
could understand.

32:41.192 --> 32:45.630 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But they never supported in the
main or for
the majority his court-packing
plan.

32:45.663 --> 32:48.132 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, it's not so
unusual, Michael.

32:48.166 --> 32:51.402 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But it is -- there has been a
frequency we
haven't seen.

32:51.436 --> 32:53.538 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MICHAEL BESCHLOSS: I think
that's right.

32:53.571 --> 32:55.873 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And Reagan talked about
unelected judges.

32:55.907 --> 33:00.778 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But in Trump's case, you have
had -- and this
is historically unusual -- two
big executive

33:00.812 --> 33:06.551 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
orders within these first 100
days, including
most recently sanctuary cities,
and earlier

33:06.584 --> 33:08.286 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
on the travel ban.

33:08.319 --> 33:13.691 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Each time, he would say, almost
in anger,
this was something that an
unelected judge

33:13.725 --> 33:16.694 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
did, or something that a
so-called judge did.

33:16.728 --> 33:20.932 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And it's sort of the opposite of
conservatism,
because one of the things that
is most fundamental

33:20.965 --> 33:27.505 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in being a conservative is
having respect
for the democratic institutions
that we think

33:27.538 --> 33:29.374 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
are important.

33:29.407 --> 33:32.443 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Let's talk,
finally, Barbara,
about what the first 100 days
tells us about

33:32.477 --> 33:34.445 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
