strong.

34:21.726 --> 34:24.095 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
And we know that he was
reelected in '96.

34:24.128 --> 34:25.963 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
So, it's not a Ouija board.

34:25.997 --> 34:30.034 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
