participate in
class.

34:37.208 --> 34:39.844 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, Trump still has many more
things on which
to be graded.

34:39.877 --> 34:41.145 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: How do you see
this first...

34:41.179 --> 34:42.146 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(CROSSTALK)

34:42.180 --> 34:44.048 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MICHAEL BESCHLOSS: I totally
agree with that.

34:44.082 --> 34:48.419 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And that is that it's a standard
that historically
doesn't tell us a lot, because
think of all

34:48.453 --> 34:51.923 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
