34:58.496 --> 35:02.533 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
None of those things happened in
the first
-- during the first 100 days.

35:02.567 --> 35:08.473 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, if we were having a great
conversation
like this 100 days into each of
those presidencies,

35:08.506 --> 35:13.244 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
