predict what
historians now think was really
turning out

35:13.277 --> 35:14.612 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
to be pivotal.

35:14.645 --> 35:16.380 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Michael
Beschloss, Barbara
Perry, thank you both.

35:16.414 --> 35:17.381 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MICHAEL BESCHLOSS: Thank you,
