36:18.876 --> 36:19.110 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
SEBASTIAN JUNGER, Director,
"Hell on Earth:
The Fall of Syria and the Rise
of ISIS": Thank

36:19.143 --> 36:20.044 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
you.

36:20.077 --> 36:21.145 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: Why make this
right now?

36:21.179 --> 36:22.947 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
SEBASTIAN JUNGER: We started
about two years
ago.

36:22.980 --> 36:28.653 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
