36:30.621 --> 36:32.757 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
ISIS is a kind of rare
phenomenon.

36:32.790 --> 36:35.326 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And we wanted to explain that to
the American
people.

36:35.359 --> 36:39.063 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
HARI SREENIVASAN: But there's a
family that
you intersperse throughout this
