36:43.501 --> 36:47.205 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
And there's a real telling clip
early on in
the film where there's a father
just trying

36:47.238 --> 36:48.306 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
